 that she looked at all of our work.

146
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:16,400
 She just yelled out, stop, enough.

147
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:18,800
 And then she said, everybody get up.

148
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:20,560
 Now, don't worry, I'm not gonna ask you to do this,

149
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:22,500
 but for us, she said, everybody get up.

150
00:06:22,500 --> 00:06:24,440
 And so we got up, and she said,

151
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:26,880
 okay, follow me around the room.

152
00:06:26,880 --> 00:06:27,840
 He said, good in twos.

153
00:06:27,840 --> 00:06:30,120
 There was eight of us, so we began to march.

154
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:34,480
 And she began to sing, dance, chant this,

155
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:39,280
 beauty to the left of me, beauty to the right of me,

156
00:06:39,280 --> 00:06:42,560
 I will always look for beauty.

157
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:46,920
 Beauty to the left of me, beauty to the right of me,

158
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:50,360
 I will always look for beauty.

159
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:52,240
 Now, you can imagine what was going through my mind

160
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:54,200
 having just left Anderson and all that.

161
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:55,800
 I'm like, where am I, right?

162
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:58,160
 This is really weird, right?

163
00:06:58,160 --> 00:07:00,560
 And the guy who was there to get his portrait

164
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:02,420
 was highly amused with all of this.

165
00:07:02,420 --> 00:07:05,260
 But she was right.

166
00:07:05,260 --> 00:07:07,720
 She was right.

167
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:10,760
 It was really weird, but she was really right.

168
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:13,760
 Because beauty is all around of us

169
00:07:13,760 --> 00:07:17,060
 for those who have eyes to see.

170
00:07:17,060 --> 00:07:21,080
 Thomas Merton, a beautiful Christian writer,

171
00:07:21,080 --> 00:07:24,240
 he was a Christian monk and poet, he said this.

172
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:28,440
 He said that every bush is on fire

173
00:07:28,440 --> 00:07:30,660
