00:24:50,660 --> 00:24:52,700
 so if your eye is healthy,

554
00:24:52,700 --> 00:24:54,980
 your whole body will be filled with light.

555
00:24:54,980 --> 00:24:58,500
 The word healthy there has this sense of generous

556
00:24:58,500 --> 00:25:02,800
 or gracious, like in a big, healthy portion

