00:26:12,500 --> 00:26:16,300
 and say, "Jesus, we want a healthy way of looking at things.

581
00:26:16,300 --> 00:26:18,900
 "We want to see you in a healthy way,

582
00:26:18,900 --> 00:26:21,660
 "and then we want to see others in that healthy way,

583
00:26:21,660 --> 00:26:24,760
 "and love God, love others, love self.

584
00:26:24,760 --> 00:26:27,540
 "We want to see ourselves in a healthy way."

585
00:26:27,540 --> 00:26:29,760
 Because if we're not seeing ourselves in a healthy way,

586
00:26:29,760 --> 00:26:32,280
 and this is a huge issue on the campuses,

587
00:26:32,280 --> 00:26:36,800
 then this will be filled with darkness as well.

588
00:26:36,800 --> 00:26:41,100
 So may God give us healthy vision to see, amen?

589
00:26:41,100 --> 00:26:43,760
 'Cause then there's that full vision,

590
00:26:43,760 --> 00:26:48,760
 and then we can see in a way that is of God,

591
00:26:49,120 --> 00:26:52,920
 that is of Jesus.

592
00:26:52,920 --> 00:27:01,180
 Abraham Lincoln was a leader in the US during the Civil War,

593
00:27:01,180 --> 00:27:06,600
 and he was known for being a leader of character.

594
00:27:06,600 --> 00:27:08,280
 Character was important to him,

