 "I don't like that man.

605
00:27:28,600 --> 00:27:30,920
 "I don't like that man."

606
00:27:30,920 --> 00:27:32,360
 And then he said to his assistant,

607
00:27:32,360 --> 00:27:34,200
 "I need to get to know him better.

608
00:27:34,200 --> 00:27:36,840
 "I don't like that man.

609
00:27:36,840 --> 00:27:38,980
 "I need to get to know him better."

610
00:27:38,980 --> 00:27:41,140
 What he's talking about there is respect,

