00:29:34,300 --> 00:29:38,060
 He says, "It's when you can look in the face

657
00:29:38,060 --> 00:29:42,420
 "of any man, any woman, any child,

658
00:29:42,420 --> 00:29:46,920
 "and see the face of your brother or your sister,

659
00:29:46,920 --> 00:29:53,580
